name: Aer Lingus A330 Business Class Dublin to JFK
description:
Watch this video to see the entire Aer Lingus experience onboard their flagship Airbus A330 from Dublin to New York’s JFK!

You’ll see everything the airline has to offer on one of their most premium routes from their home at Dublin to New York City.

This video highlights everything from the Aer Lingus Business Class check-in experience to the Aer Lingus Business Class lounge in Dublin. You’ll even see everything onboard from the industry leading Aer Lingus Business Class “throne” seat and the Aer Lingus food. You’ll see the inflight entertainment from Aer Lingus and so much more.

0:00 Introduction
2:07 Aer Lingus Business Class Lounge
3:28 Boarding Aer Lingus A330
7:52 Aer Lingus Business Class Lunch
10:00 Aer Lingus JebScore
